Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:46.85,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H99}By now, it seems we’ve come to realize that…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:52.06,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H99}The ideas of a revolving world, a withering, blazing sun above
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:57.22,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H99}The heat-haze shimmered; “Don’t forget - now, move on…”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:03:02.35,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H99}Filled with impatience, we dreamt repeatedly of tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:07.52,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H99}No going back, but to the world ahead; “We’ll change it…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:12.72,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H33\c&H99A3A1&}"Remember, it’s all over. Our secret base, our adventure…"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:18.02,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,0)\blur3\3a&H33\c&H99A3A1&}And when we were lost that day, those stories as well…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:25.31,Bottom,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,150)\blur3\3a&H33\c&H99A3A1&}Those children, all alone, gathered to make a plan, and again today, it went into motion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.85,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,590)\fs90\t(0,100,\fs60)\t(100,1130,\fs55)\fade(100,100)\blur3\3a&H88}“May we find each other again.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:33.06,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,585)\fs90\t(0,125,\fs60)\t(125,4688,\fs50)\t(4688,4790,\fs20)\fade(100,100)\blur3\3a&H88\c&HF5FBFA&}"Refreshing," we said together; the summer sky is crystal clear
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:38.14,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,585)\fs90\t(0,125,\fs60)\t(125,4693,\fs50)\t(4693,4750,\fs20)\fade(100,0)\blur3\3a&H88\c&HF5FBFA&}Let’s breathe in, trying not to cry, and say our goodbyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:41.18,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\t(0,125,\fs60)\t(125,2380,\fs50)\t(2380,2460,\fs20)\fade(100,100)\blur3\3a&H88\pos(355,580)}Gathered at our secret base,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.77,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\t(0,125,\fs60)\t(125,2400,\fs50)\t(2400,2500,\fs20)\fade(100,100)\blur3\3a&H88\pos(1560,580)}we laughed that summer day;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.35,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\t(0,125,\fs60)\t(125,2390,\fs50)\t(2390,2500,\fs20)\fade(100,100)\blur3\3a&H88\pos(355,580)}“Remember it somewhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.10,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\t(0,125,\fs60)\t(125,2600,\fs50)\t(2600,2670,\fs20)\fade(100,100)\blur3\3a&H88\pos(1560,580)}and perhaps we’ll meet again…”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:54.31,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\t(0,150,\fs60)\t(150,5130,\fs45)\fade(100,1000)\blur3\3a&H88\move(1000,595,1000,585)}So I’ll {\c&HD8E506&}draw {\c&HD6DADE&}it,　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　　again and again…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:07.14,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3a&H33\fade(500,1000)\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF\bord0.1\fs50\pos(960,430)}『Kagerou Project』
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:07.14,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(500,1000)\blur2\3c&HFFFFFF\3a&H33\bord0.1\fs70\pos(960,650)}Summer Time Record
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:08.64,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\c&HA1BEB9&}"I guess it must be goodbye, now."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:08.81,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"You won’t forget again, will you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:08.97,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"Don’t worry. I couldn’t forget a tale like this."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:09.14,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"I wonder about that. I bet you’ll have completely forgotten by tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:09.31,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"And is that so bad? I mean, if there are better days to come…"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.31,0:04:09.47,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"But we’ll meet again somewhere, won’t we?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:09.64,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"Of course we will. Well, I’d better be going now."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:09.81,Middle,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fade(100,0)\3a&H88\pos(960,588)\fn小塚ゴシック Pr6N M\c&HA1BEB9&}"Right. I’ll see you later."
